      • getDBAppointments

        public static void getDBAppointments()
        The getDBAppointments() method. This method clears data out of the observable list allAppointments and then uses a select statement to pull in all of the appointment data that is stored in the database. It will then create appointment objects and add those objects back into the allAppointments list.
